#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Service Manager</guilabel> module allows you to have an "
"overview of all plugins of the &kde; Daemon, also referred to as &kde; "
"Services. Generally, there are two types of service:"
msgstr ""
"Modul <guilabel>Upravitelj storitev </guilabel> omogoča pregled nad vsemi "
"vtičniki sistema &kde; Daemon, imenovanimi tudi &kde; Services. Na splošno "
"obstajata dve vrsti storitev:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Load-on-Demand Services"
msgstr "Storitve nalaganja na zahtevo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a list of available &kde; services which will be started on demand. "
"They are only listed for convenience, as you cannot manipulate these "
"services."
msgstr ""
"To je seznam razpoložljivih storitev &kde;, ki se zaženejo na zahtevo. "
"Navedene so le zaradi priročnosti, saj s temi storitvami ne morete "
"upravljati."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup Services"
msgstr "Storitve zagona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This shows all &kde; services that can be loaded on &kde; startup. Services "
"checked in the <guilabel>Use</guilabel> column will be invoked on next "
"startup."
msgstr ""
"To prikazuje vse storitve &kde;, ki jih je mogoče naložiti ob zagonu &kde;. "
"Storitve, označene v stolpcu <guilabel>Uporabi</guilabel>, bodo sprožene ob "
"naslednjem zagonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be careful with deactivation of unknown services: some services are vital "
"for &kde;; do not deactivate services if you do not know what you are doing."
msgstr ""
"Bodite previdni pri deaktivaciji neznanih storitev: nekatere storitve so "
"ključnega pomena za &kde;; ne deaktivirajte storitev, če ne veste, kaj "
"počnete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the <guilabel>Status</guilabel> of a service, select it in the "
"list. Then you can use the <guibutton>Start</guibutton> and <guibutton>Stop</"
"guibutton> to change the status of a service from <guilabel>Not running</"
"guilabel> to <guilabel>Running</guilabel> and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti <guilabel>Status</guilabel> storitve, jo izberite na "
"seznamu. Nato lahko z gumboma <guibutton>Začetek</guibutton> in "
"<guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton> spremenite stanje storitve iz <guilabel>Ne "
"deluje</guilabel> v <guilabel>Poteka</guilabel> in obratno."
